==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mitrewort
<hw>mitrewort</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of various rhizomatous
perennial herbs of the genus <gen>Mitella</gen> having a capsule
resembling a bishop's miter.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>miterwort</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> miterwort, bishop's cap.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mitriform</ent>⟦br⟧
